### 사용자 설정 API (User Settings)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api

### ===========================================
### 사용자 설정 조회/수정
### ===========================================

### 내 설정 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 설정 수정 (테마 색상, 정원 배경)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "themeColor": "blue",
  "themeGardenBg": "spring"
}

### 설정 수정 (테마 색상만)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "themeColor": "pink",
  "themeGardenBg": "default"
}

### 설정 수정 (정원 배경만)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "themeColor": "yellow",
  "themeGardenBg": "winter"
}
